China Windpower Group Hires HSBC Holdings to Issue Yuan-Denominated Bonds

-- B y   S t a n l e y   J a m e s
-- 
2011-03-21T22:36:48Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-03-21/china-windpower-group-hires-hsbc-holdings-to-issue-yuan-denominated-bonds.html
China WindPower Group Ltd. (182)  plans to
issue yuan-denominated bonds, the company said in a statement to
the Hong Kong stock exchange today. The amount, terms and
conditions of the bonds are yet to be decided, it said. HSBC
Holdings Plc is the sole lead manager of the issue, according to
China Windpower.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Stanley James at 
 sjames8@bloomberg.net  